1
00:00:14,370 --> 00:00:17,370
Peaceful starry summer night.

2
00:00:18,820 --> 00:00:21,300
While listening to
the chirping of cicadas,

3
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:23,670
I used to make unrealistic dreams.

4
00:00:25,060 --> 00:00:26,590
Even though it is a dream,

5
00:00:26,870 --> 00:00:28,620
I always remind myself

6
00:00:28,850 --> 00:00:30,280
not to believe it.

7
00:00:31,530 --> 00:00:33,340
I'm still insignificant.

8
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:42,360
After I get up every morning,

9
00:00:42,420 --> 00:00:43,800
I walk in the hallway

10
00:00:44,490 --> 00:00:46,340
of a grand villa in a nice dress.

11
00:00:46,890 --> 00:00:48,290
The scent of the flowers

12
00:00:48,330 --> 00:00:49,910
refreshes me from drowsy.

13
00:00:50,830 --> 00:00:53,950
The music wakes up my brain from idle.

14
00:00:54,480 --> 00:00:57,090
The servants are caring,

15
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:00,340
the elders always attentive.

16
00:01:01,490 --> 00:01:04,370
Guess it's every girl's princess dream.

17
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:06,940
In fact,

18
00:01:06,980 --> 00:01:08,400
it's also a dream

19
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,690
for me,

20
00:01:10,340 --> 00:01:11,620
but more like a nightmare.

21
00:01:19,510 --> 00:01:25,410
[Two days ago]

22
00:01:26,740 --> 00:01:28,620
Chu Xia!

23
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:30,620
Let me deliver the milk today.

24
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,920
I can do it alone.

25
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,480
Okay?

26
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:34,990
You're not the Monkey King,
can't be a tailor cum dispatch.

27
00:01:35,010 --> 00:01:36,660
It will be yogurt when it's sent.

28
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:38,710
Since you don't want to study,

29
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,720
I don't have to work part-time then.

30
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,130
You'll be exhausted
if I don't bother.

31
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:45,110
Let's talk about the study later.

32
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,940
We have to make money now.

33
00:01:47,010 --> 00:01:47,860
Okay?

34
00:01:48,190 --> 00:01:49,660
