35
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,400
My pendant.

36
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:53,010
Why don't we

37
00:01:53,180 --> 00:01:55,570
borrow some money from Meng Xiao Nan?

38
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,930
It's been a month since she left.

39
00:01:57,990 --> 00:02:01,030
It's not sensible if we
borrow money from her

40
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,910
the moment she gets rich.

41
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:03,920
I'm off.

42
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:04,900
Hey!

43
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:06,520
With that wearing?

44
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,620
Give it to me!

45
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:17,330
No way!

46
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,490
Give it to me!

47
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,240
No way!

48
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,770
-Give it to me!
-No way!

49
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,630
Zhang Xiao Ming.

50
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:24,930
What's up?

51
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:27,600
Don't mess around here!

52
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:31,950
Xiao Ying, come here.

53
00:02:32,530 --> 00:02:33,640
Xiao Ying.

54
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,650
Girls should know martial art.

55
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:37,010
I'll teach you next time.

56
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,790
Okay.

57
00:02:38,150 --> 00:02:39,140
Thank you.

58
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:39,700
Go ahead.

59
