132
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:17,690
Too bad.

133
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:22,510
Young Master Han was kissing
with a girl on the street.

134
00:08:23,650 --> 00:08:24,780
Cut the crap.

135
00:08:24,860 --> 00:08:25,910
Anything I can help?

136
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:27,450
About the military training.

137
00:08:27,450 --> 00:08:28,580
Let's talk in the car.

138
00:08:33,330 --> 00:08:35,000
Don't go!

139
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,060
Here you are.

140
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:48,110
Enough?

141
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,760
Maybe...

142
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:53,290
Take it all.

143
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,570
That's enough.

144
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,800
Alright, I'm off.

145
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,310
Bye!

146
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:09,520
My pendant is in his bag.

147
00:09:25,490 --> 00:09:27,220
I got up so early today.

148
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:28,820
What the hell is this?

149
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,250
What's the point of the military training?

150
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:32,660
It's a remote area.

151
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:36,630
Listen, Class A and B!

152
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:39,960
The main purpose
of this military training

153
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,960
is to strengthen your physique

154
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,660
and sharpen your determination.

155
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:49,860
-What's this?
-Use the social knowledge...

156
00:09:49,930 --> 00:09:52,420
All the students?

157
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:54,050
Where are Han Qi Lu and Ling Han Yu?

158
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,910
Ling Han Yu went to find Han Qi Lu.

159
00:09:56,450 --> 00:09:57,830
I didn't ask you.

160
00:10:02,190 --> 00:10:03,440
Xin Wei.

161
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:05,600
Since when have you become
interested in astronomy?

162
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:08,100
I'm interested in nothing but Qi Lu.

163
00:10:09,010 --> 00:10:10,850
Where's the milk?

164
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:17,160
Principal! We haven't got the milk!

165
00:10:17,170 --> 00:10:20,910
Yeah! We haven't got the milk!

166
00:10:22,410 --> 00:10:24,110
Quickly call them.

167
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:38,930
[Caution! Under consideration]

168
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:03,550
Hello.

169
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,050
Why didn't you send the milk?

170
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,320
It hasn't arrived yet?

171
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:12,520
No matter who sends it,
quickly get it done!

172
00:11:12,590 --> 00:11:15,310
Okay, I'll send it now.

173
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,200
Missing the kiss?

174
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:38,910
My illness seems healed.

175
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,480
My mouth no longer swollen.

176
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:46,220
A weirdo must be healed by a weirdo.

177
00:11:49,130 --> 00:11:51,010
Speak of the devil.

178
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:55,760
So macho!

179
00:11:55,780 --> 00:11:57,320
Stop!

180
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:02,380
Give me the pendant!

181
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:24,060
What's wrong?

182
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,290
Come out.

183
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:40,020
Hurry up!

184
00:12:40,050 --> 00:12:40,940
You two.

185
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,000
What's going on?

186
00:12:44,580 --> 00:12:45,740
Hurry.

187
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,080
Hurry up.

188
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:52,060
Stop!

189
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:57,470
One more.

190
00:12:58,090 --> 00:12:59,480
Hey, you! Super Saiyan!

191
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,760
Come on!

192
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,680
Come on!

193
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:06,060
Come on!

194
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:08,600
Hurry up.

195
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:10,300
Come on!

196
00:13:11,450 --> 00:13:12,070
Come on!

197
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:18,720
Hand in everything.

198
00:13:21,760 --> 00:13:24,380
-Call the police.
-No signal.

199
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:25,740
You deserved it.

200
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:30,520
My pendant fell into his bag
when I was falling down.

201
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:32,640
When you two were kissing?

202
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,790
Just a pendant.

203
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:36,000
Buy it for her.

204
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,880
You can't buy it with money.

205
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,490
Give it back to me and I'll leave.

206
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:43,880
The bag's over there.

207
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:45,930
Can you get it?

208
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:47,740
Can you leave?

209
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:49,030
Give it to me!

210
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,970
They are coming.

211
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:52,270
You can't run away.

212
00:13:52,830 --> 00:13:54,340
I won't help you even if I make it.

213
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:57,360
Hand it over!

214
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:02,150
I'll give you 1.1 million yuan
if you call the police.

215
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,590
Call what?

216
00:14:05,850 --> 00:14:06,830
Idiot.

217
00:14:16,800 --> 00:14:18,650
I'm here to deliver the milk.

218
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:21,750
