219
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:23,640
Where's the milk?

220
00:14:24,550 --> 00:14:26,210
It was spilled because of him.

221
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,620
You slept with him?

222
00:14:27,660 --> 00:14:28,600
They kissed.

223
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:29,970
It was spilled.

224
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,220
You spilled the milk?

225
00:14:31,260 --> 00:14:31,880
