226
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,780
-Why are you here then?
-To get something.

227
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:35,070
-What?
-Something money can't buy.

228
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,760
-What?
-A pendant.

229
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:38,430
Don't speak at the same time.

230
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:39,650
Okay.

231
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:13,350
