243
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,590
We want cash.

244
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:48,310
Bro!

245
00:15:48,340 --> 00:15:49,790
What are you doing? Come back!

246
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:51,000
Bro!

247
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:52,750
How do I address you?

248
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,550
What are you doing?

249
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:55,810
How do I address you?

250
00:15:55,850 --> 00:15:57,350
I'm a gangster too.

251
00:15:57,360 --> 00:16:02,010
I'm An Chu Xia, the head of
Huo Ni Hall in Cat Ears Lane.

252
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:04,500
-Let's be friends.
-Straight to the point!

253
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:05,810
No money.

254
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:09,300
She's here to deliver the milk.

255
00:16:11,230 --> 00:16:12,590
You are the dispatch, huh?

256
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:14,460
Be punctual in the future.

257
00:16:14,490 --> 00:16:17,860
-Be careful when you go downhill.
-Okay.

258
00:16:20,010 --> 00:16:21,180
Bye!

259
00:16:21,180 --> 00:16:22,200
Be careful.

260
00:16:22,350 --> 00:16:23,540
They let her go.

261
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:25,670
-Bye.
-Be careful.

262
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:27,800
Be punctual in the future.

263
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,560
