264
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:35,240
"Call the police"

265
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:40,450
I'll give you 1.1 million yuan
if you call the police.

266
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,440
What's up?

267
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,590
