272
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:59,060
Give me back the pendant!

273
00:16:59,530 --> 00:17:01,020
What pendant?

274
00:17:02,210 --> 00:17:04,270
Is the 1.1 million yuan still effective?

275
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:05,260
Sure.

276
00:17:06,330 --> 00:17:08,670
My pendant is in your bag.

277
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:10,990
Give me the money.

278
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:13,620
My bag is not here.

279
00:17:14,150 --> 00:17:15,150
Not now.

280
00:17:15,180 --> 00:17:17,450
-Go and get the bag!
-The time is almost up.

281
00:17:17,450 --> 00:17:18,790
-So fast.
-We can't carry on.

282
00:17:19,320 --> 00:17:21,020
Pay me the deposit first.

283
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:23,860
We want to get our bags.

284
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:26,360
